article.description: — Nicolas Timberlake had 24 points as Towson topped Navy 69-52 on Wednesday.
article.headline: Timberlake scores 24 to carry Towson past Navy 69-52
article.linkText: Timberlake scores 24 to carry Towson past Navy 69-52
article.story: ANNAPOLIS, Md. -- — Nicolas Timberlake had 24 points as Towson topped Navy 69-52 on Wednesday. Timberlake hit 9 of 12 shots, including 5 of 6 on 3-pointers. Charles Thompson had 10 points, eight rebounds and five blocks for Towson (9-4). Cam Holden added eight rebounds, and Terry Nolan Jr. had eight assists. Jaylen Walker had 13 points for the Midshipmen (7-4). Greg Summers added 12 points and 10 rebounds. Richard Njoku had 10 rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
